BT /F1 16 Tf 36 768 Td (VendHub OS - One-Page App Summary \(Repo Evidence\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 36 742 Td (What it is) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 728 Td (- VendHub OS is a monorepo platform for vending operations in Uzbekistan.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 715 Td (- It combines a NestJS API with admin web, client PWA, mobile app, and Telegram bot.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 36 694 Td (Who it's for) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 680 Td (- Primary persona: franchise owners/admins, operators, warehouse and accounting teams.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 36 659 Td (What it does) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 645 Td (- Multi-tenant RBAC \(owner/admin/manager/accountant/operator/warehouse/viewer\).) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 632 Td (- Manages machines, products, locations, inventory, tasks, and maintenance workflows.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 619 Td (- Supports client engagement: loyalty, quests, referrals, favorites, recommendations.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 606 Td (- Integrates payments/fiscal flows \(Payme, Click, Uzum, Telegram, OFD hooks\).) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 593 Td (- Sends notifications via Telegram, SMS, email, web push, and FCM modules.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 580 Td (- Provides reporting, analytics, import pipelines, and audit/security modules.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 36 559 Td (How it works \(repo-based architecture\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 545 Td (- Frontends: apps/web \(Next.js\), apps/client \(Vite\), apps/site \(Next.js\), apps/mobile \(Expo\).) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 532 Td (- Bot: apps/bot \(Telegraf\). Backend: apps/api \(NestJS, app.module imports 77 modules\).) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 519 Td (- Runtime stack from docker-compose: nginx -> api -> postgres/redis/minio + bull-board.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 506 Td (- API data layer: TypeORM + PostgreSQL; cache/session and queues use Redis/BullMQ.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 493 Td (- Data flow: clients/bot -> API -> Postgres \(core data\), Redis \(cache/jobs\), MinIO \(files\).) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 480 Td (- Detailed IoT device protocol/telemetry ingestion path: Not found in repo.) Tj ET
BT /F1 12 Tf 36 459 Td (How to run \(minimal getting started\)) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 445 Td (1. cp .env.example .env and set required secrets \(DB/JWT/STORAGE vars\).) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 432 Td (2. docker-compose up -d postgres redis minio) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 419 Td (3. pnpm install && pnpm db:migrate && pnpm db:seed) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 406 Td (4. pnpm dev) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 44 393 Td (5. Open: API 4000/docs, Admin 3000, Client 5173, Site 3100.) Tj ET
